title: Ivan Prieto Nutriologo | Nutritionist website
description: This is a project built with Next js and CSS, mobile responsive. It has a main page with the nutritionist info, appointment information to get customers, followed by pretty layout of images, then an example of a diet table, and testimonies at the end. It also has a contact page that works with email js for users to book appointments and the nutritionist Ivan receives them in his email inbox
